observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Management:
Direct the Municipal Budget Officer to submit a written explanation on certifying that the existence of appropriation has been legally made for the purpose despite the pending approval of the Budget Supplemental and realignment of savings;
Require the Municipal Budget Officer to limit disbursement of funds to what has been duly appropriated in the annual and supplemental budget to avoid incurrence of overdraft;
Henceforth, charge the expenditure according to its nature and purpose during the budget preparation and adhere to the rules and regulations and other pertinent provision in granting leave credit monetization.

